"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-06-Shanghai-embraces-Olympic-spirit-with-mini-Games--1vQl5LUXIbu-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  CGTN  Copied  Amid the Paris Olympics, Shanghai is embracing the Olympic spirit through a mini-Olympics event and virtual sports competitions. In RuihongTiandi district, the city is offering a diverse range of sports activities. Meanwhile, the Shanghai Virtual Sports Open features elite rowing contests. This fusion of amateur and professional events underscores Shanghai's dedication to promoting athleticism and innovation in sports, echoing the global excitement surrounding the Olympics.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"